title: Aaya vo jagat mein
lyrics:
Aaya vo jagat mein, paapiyon ko karne paritran
Laya vo jeevan deep sansar ko karne ujjala -2
Marg vahi, satya vahi, jeevan bhi vahi hai -2
(A)
Vo vahi Masi hai jo aane wala
Vo vahi Masi hai jo bachane wala -2
Swarg uska, dharti bhi, sabka vahi hai rakha wala
(B)
Dukh uthaya Prabhu ne, taaki hamen mukti mile
Balidan hua Ishu ne, taise hamen jeevan mile-2
Mukti vahi hai, jeevan bhi, sabka vahi hai rakha wala
